4Geeks Academy offers a course on becoming an AI Machine Learning Engineer. With no previous knowledge required, students can start a career as a data scientist and build their first ML models. The course is 16 weeks long, with 3 classes weekly and a maximum class size of 12 people. The instructors have extensive experience in AI and machine learning, with PhDs in Artificial Intelligence and Robotics & Artificial Intelligence. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and industry-standard tools. Students will learn to create predictive models and work with supervised and unsupervised learning algorithms. They will also practice solving real-life cases and develop their own AI projects. The course is available in English and Spanish. Upon completion, students will receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit their website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop